Azure Rest API Specifications

This page provides an inventory of all Azure Rest API Specifications from azure-rest-api-specs repo. The Data plane TypeSpec and Management TypeSpecs only show services that have a TypeSpec defined. The all table shows all the specs both TypeSpec and OpenAPI.
